# fyipedia — Unified CLI Demo
Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 920
Set Height 620
Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Padding 20

Type "fyi version"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "fyi color info FF6B35"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "fyi unit convert 100 kilometer mile"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s
